title: Wholesale Price of Amoskeag Ginghams, Factory for United States
notes:
Series Has Been Subdivided Into 2 Variables: (1) -- Original Data, 1890-1936; (2) -- Original Data, 1931-1941. Data Refers To The Price At The Factory On The First Of The Month Of Amoskeag Gingham, 7 Inches Wide, 6.37 Yards To The Pound. Source: Bls Bulletins And Monthly Issues Of "Wholesale Prices"

This NBER data series m04075 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
